---
layout: layout.njk
title: "About — Gripmode"
metaDesc: "Gripmode was built by martial arts school operators who were frustrated with bloated, expensive software. Learn our story and mission."
breadcrumbs:
  - { name: "Home", url: "/" }
  - { name: "About", url: "/about/" }
---

{% block extraHead %}
<style>
  :root{
    --bg:#ffffff;--bg-soft:#f7f8fa;--text:#0f1115;--muted:#5f6672;--line:#e5e7eb;--black:#111315;--radius:16px;--dark-bg:#0f1114;
  }
  section{padding:88px 0}
  .about-hero{padding:96px 0 72px;max-width:760px}
  .about-hero .eyebrow{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:7px 12px;border-radius:999px;background:#f4f4f5;border:1px solid var(--line);font-size:.83rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:24px}
  .sub{font-size:1.14rem;color:var(--muted);max-width:60ch;line-height:1.7}
  .story-section{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:48px;align-items:start}
  .story-section h2{margin-bottom:20px}
  .story-section p{color:var(--muted);font-size:1.02rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0 0 16px}
  .mission-block{background:var(--bg-soft);border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:36px}
  .mission-block h3{font-family:"Space Grotesk",sans-serif;font-size:1.4rem;margin-bottom:14px}
  .mission-block p{color:var(--muted);font-size:1.04rem;line-height:1.7;margin:0}
  .values-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:18px;margin-top:32px}
  .value-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:24px;transition:transform .2s,box-shadow .2s}
  .value-card:hover{transform:translateY(-4px);box-shadow:0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)}
  .value-card h3{font-family:"Space Grotesk",sans-serif;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:8px}
  .value-card p{color:var(--muted);font-size:.92rem;margin:0;line-height:1.6}
  .value-card .icon{width:22px;height:22px;stroke-width:2.1;margin-bottom:12px}
  .team-section{background:var(--bg-soft);padding:88px 0}
  .team-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:24px;margin-top:32px}
  .team-card{background:#fff;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:var(--radius);padding:28px;display:flex;gap:20px;align-items:start}
  .team-avatar{width:64px;height:64px;background:var(--black);border-radius:50%;display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-weight:700;font-size:1.2rem;flex-shrink:0}
  .team-info h3{font-family:"Space Grotesk",sans-serif;font-size:1.1rem;margin-bottom:4px}
  .team-info .team-role{font-size:.9rem;color:var(--muted);margin-bottom:10px}
  .team-info p{color:var(--muted);font-size:.92rem;margin:0;line-height:1.6}
  @media (max-width:980px){
    section{padding:66px 0}
    .story-section,.values-grid,.team-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}
    .team-section{padding:66px 0}
  }
</style>
{% endblock %}

<div class="gm-container">
  <section class="about-hero">
    <span class="eyebrow"><i data-lucide="users" style="width:16px;height:16px"></i> Our Story</span>
    <h1>Built by Operators,<br>for Operators</h1>
    <p class="sub">Gripmode exists because we lived the problem. We ran martial arts schools, struggled with the same broken tools, and decided to build something better.</p>
  </section>

  <section style="padding-top:0">
    <div class="story-section">
      <div>
        <h2>The Founding Story</h2>
        <p>We started as martial arts school owners -- running classes, managing instructors, chasing down payments, and drowning in spreadsheets. The software options available were either overpriced enterprise platforms built for generic gyms, or cobbled-together tools that never quite fit how a martial arts school actually operates.</p>
        <p>Every month, we dealt with payroll errors, missed retention signals, and hours lost to administrative busywork. We knew there had to be a better way.</p>
        <p>So we built Gripmode -- a focused operational system designed specifically for martial arts schools. Not a Swiss-army-knife platform that tries to do everything poorly, but a disciplined tool that does the essential things exceptionally well.</p>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="mission-block">
          <h3>Our Mission</h3>
          <p>Give every martial arts school -- from a single-location academy to a growing network -- the operational tools that only large chains could previously afford. We believe disciplined operations should be accessible, affordable, and built for practitioners.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mission-block" style="margin-top:18px">
          <h3>What We Believe</h3>
          <p>Great martial arts instruction deserves great operational support. When the business side runs smoothly, instructors can focus on what matters most: teaching, mentoring, and growing their students.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section>
    <h2>Our Values</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:1.04rem;max-width:600px">These principles guide every feature we build and every decision we make.</p>
    <div class="values-grid">
      <article class="value-card">
        <i data-lucide="shield" class="icon"></i>
        <h3>Discipline</h3>
        <p>We build focused tools, not bloated platforms. Every feature earns its place through real operator feedback.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="value-card">
        <i data-lucide="eye" class="icon"></i>
        <h3>Transparency</h3>
        <p>Simple pricing, clear communication, no hidden fees. You always know exactly what you're getting and what you're paying.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="value-card">
        <i data-lucide="zap" class="icon"></i>
        <h3>Simplicity</h3>
        <p>If it takes more than five minutes to learn, we've failed. Gripmode should feel intuitive from day one.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="value-card">
        <i data-lucide="heart" class="icon"></i>
        <h3>Practitioner-First</h3>
        <p>We're martial artists building for martial artists. Every decision is filtered through the lens of real school operations.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</div>

<section class="team-section">
  <div class="gm-container">
    <h2>The Team</h2>
    <p style="color:var(--muted);font-size:1.04rem;max-width:600px">A small, focused team of operators and engineers building the tools we wish we had.</p>
    <div class="team-grid">
      <article class="team-card">
        <div class="team-avatar">FM</div>
        <div class="team-info">
          <h3>Founder</h3>
          <div class="team-role">CEO & Product</div>
          <p>Martial arts school operator turned software builder. Obsessed with removing friction from daily school operations.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
      <article class="team-card">
        <div class="team-avatar">CO</div>
        <div class="team-info">
          <h3>Co-Founder</h3>
          <div class="team-role">CTO & Engineering</div>
          <p>Full-stack engineer with a background in building operational tools. Believes great software should disappear into the workflow.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<div class="gm-container">
  {% include "cta-section.njk" %}
</div>
